window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>His name is Taylor McFadden, survivor of eighty-three trips into the ZOO. Now he's retired, and yet his country still needs his skills to save people in the country he calls home.</p> <p>Can he build a company, put down roots, and still bring the pain when the FBI calls?</p> <p>When they tag him as The Cryptid Assassin, they weren't wrong. For monsters that go bump in the night, he is death incarnate.</p>"; 
